看本质，新的技术会一直持续下去，但没有对技术本质的把握，永远也是被动的学习及低效的努力。<br><br>过了技术这一个门槛，后面的路途会更宽敞明亮，思路也应该会更宽阔，这时我们做技术的主人，做时代的幸运儿。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":58769,"user_name":"林锋","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1102487,"ip_address":"","ucode":"DA982AD20261F5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/d2/97/49e748f2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1547190286,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1547190286","product_id":100020201,"comment_content":"智慧老师的文章就是写的很有乐趣，以前《大型网站技术架构：核心原理与案例分析》就对老师很感谢，让我真正进入了互联网思维。看了这个系列又刚好补进我的大数据思维，技术思考确实太重要了。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":41665,"user_name":"hunterlodge","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1069755,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5B83A79E784161","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/52/bb/225e70a6.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542817032,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1542817032","product_id":100020201,"comment_content":"这样的阶段总结和回顾实在再贴心不过，老师分享自己独到的经验更是弥足珍贵，谢谢老师！也谢谢学友们的分享，很多留言重看一遍还是多有受益。P.S 竟然被老师翻牌了！哈哈哈","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":40735,"user_name":"多襄丸","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1074310,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1AA1497C5A293C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/64/86/f5a9403a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542673044,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1542673044","product_id":100020201,"comment_content":"最后那段代码有哪位师哥解释下呗？（感激……）","like_count":0}]}